<item>
            <title>[LU-11417] Add llapi_layout_get_by_xattr() interface</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11417</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The code in &lt;tt&gt;llapi_layout_get_by_fd()&lt;/tt&gt; should be abstracted into a new &lt;tt&gt;llapi_layout_get_by_xattr()&lt;/tt&gt; helper function, which is used by the upper layers and can also be used on a &lt;tt&gt;&quot;lov&quot;&lt;/tt&gt; xattr regardless of how it is obtained. That is useful if the xattr has been fetched from some other method, or a tarball or HSM archive, etc. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
